dcterms:description: A benchmark dataset containing 135,000 image pairs, each consisting of an image contaminated with a moiré pattern and its corresponding uncontaminated reference image. The reference images are taken from the ImageNet dataset.
dcterms:title: Moiré Pattern Removal Dataset

dcterms:description: The ImageNet ISVRC 2012 dataset is used as the source for the uncontaminated reference images in the Moiré Pattern Removal Dataset.
dcterms:title: ImageNet ISVRC 2012 dataset
